# Agent Global Hub

Canonical source of truth for shared agent configuration. Claude, Kilo Code, and Antigravity all read from here via symlinks.

**Rule**: Edit files HERE. Symlinks propagate changes to all agents automatically.

## Structure

```
~/.agent_global/
├── rules/global_rules.md          → symlinked to Claude + Kilo + Antigravity
├── workflows/
│   ├── core-directives.md         → symlinked to Claude + Kilo + Antigravity
│   ├── commit-protocol.md         → symlinked to Claude + Kilo + Antigravity
│   ├── memory-bank-protocol.md    → symlinked to Claude + Kilo + Antigravity
│   └── documentation-sync.md      → symlinked to Claude + Kilo + Antigravity
├── skills/
│   ├── mcp-builder/               → symlinked to ~/.kilocode/skills/
│   └── skill-creator/             → symlinked to ~/.kilocode/skills/
├── templates/memory-bank/         → Bootstrap template for new projects
├── bootstrap-project.sh           → Script to setup new projects
└── SETUP.md                       → Setup guide for new projects
```

